hnical competence, performance under pressure, decision\u2011making, teamwork/communication, and long\u2011term suitability), **Candidate\u202fB** offers the most balanced profile. His technical and cognitive strengths, together with proven stress handling, outweigh the relatively minor interpersonal shortcomings, which seem manageable compared with the more serious deficits of the other candidates.\n**My vote:** Candidate B\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
